  "title": "Account Executive",
  "description": "<p>1. Handle administrative duties, data entry and filling</p>\n<p>2. Assist in the daily major accounting functions</p>\n<p>3. Assist in any ad-hoc duties and creativities as and when required</p>\n<p>4. Preparation of monthly account reconciliations, including bank reconciliations</p>\n<p>5. Take on all accounting functions: payables, receivables, banking, taxes, audit preparation and etc.</p>\n<p>6. Ensure all statutory filings and other compliance formalities are completed in a timely manner</p>\n<p>7. Preparation of invoice and purchase order</p>\n<p>8. Preparing and analyzing financial statements, managing cash flow, ensuring compliance with tax regulations, and overseeing the accounting operations of our company.</p>\n<p>9. Prepare and review monthly, quarterly, and annual financial statements and reports</p>\n<p><br></p>",
